[I] Compiler for the C3 language

[T] C3 is a programming language that builds on the syntax and semantics of the
[T] C language, with the goal of evolving it while still retaining familiarity
[T] for C programmers. It's an evolution, not a revolution: the C-like for
[T] programmers who like C.

[U] https://c3-lang.org/

[A] Christoffer Lerno <christoffer@aegik.com>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/development
[F] OBJDIR

[L] LGPL
[V] 0.8.0

